Author: scaredyk4t
Text: I just always feel “embarrassed” when I see on this sub when people post about a binge that’s basically 100-300 cals over their normal intake when my binges consist of at least 3000 cals. I will literally eat myself sick and I’m still feeling the pain and so full the next day.   I’ll eat my planned out dinner. Then make a sandwich. Then ice cream. Then fruit. Then apples with pbfit. Oh okay I need more pbfit to finish the Apple. Why not just finish the pint of ice cream? Something salty sounds nice, I’ll have a grilled cheese!!   I don’t want to invalidate anyone’s experience but it’s something I’ve noticed.
